Diamond::
She looked at Devilduer. "Thank you commander."  She gently brushed 
her hand across his cheek. Then she turned and stepped into the CR 
chamber.

Squizzy:
She activated the chambers and sighed. "Commander, they will be in 
there for a little bit.  That other one is badly hurt and will take a 
while longer.  Would you like me to activate the Allience program for 
the new three?"







In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::DevilDuer/Bloodystrike/Reptilica::
> 
> Bloodystrike nods, slinging Life over his other shoulder and
> motioning 
> for Amp to follow. He sets off after Squizzy, entering the CR room.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> DevilDuer grins at Diamond's last comment, blushing a bit. "Well, 
ya 
> made quite an entrance here. Gave us lotsa scrap metal t' use in 
the 
> future."
> 
> They reach the CR chambers at the same time that Bloodystrike 
enters. 
> Bloodystrike walks to the CR chambers, putting Life in one and 
> Reptilica in the other. DevilDuer motions to the remaining CR.
> 
> "That one's for ya to use," he says, "Ya'll be out in no time, then
> we 
> can get ya registered as an Alliance member an' all."
